{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AwEy914EdQ248uWsBaxajq","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: graphql-skill\n     3→description: \"GraphQL 스키마 및 리졸버 작성 가이드\"\n     4→---\n     5→\n     6→# GraphQL Skill\n     7→\n     8→## 설명\n     9→\n    10→GraphQL 스키마 정의부터 Controller/Service 구현까지의 워크플로우를 안내한다.\n    11→\n    12→## 실행 절차\n    13→\n    14→### 1. Schema 정의\n    15→\n    16→위치: `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/schema.graphqls` 또는 별도 `.graphqls` 파일\n    17→\n    18→```graphql\n    19→type Feature {\n    20→    id: ID!\n    21→    name: String!\n    22→    user: SimpleUser\n    23→    createdAt: String!\n    24→}\n    25→\n    26→input CreateFeatureInput {\n    27→    name: String!\n    28→}\n    29→\n    30→extend type Query {\n    31→    feature(featureId: ID!): Feature\n    32→    features(limit: Int, offset: Int): [Feature!]!\n    33→}\n    34→\n    35→extend type Mutation {\n    36→    createFeature(input: CreateFeatureInput!): Feature!\n    37→    deleteFeature(featureId: ID!): Boolean!\n    38→}\n    39→```\n    40→\n    41→### 2. GraphQL Controller\n    42→\n    43→위치: `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/{도메인}/`\n    44→\n    45→```kotlin\n    46→@Controller\n    47→class FeatureController(\n    48→    private val featureService: FeatureService,\n    49→    private val userService: UserService,\n    50→) {\n    51→    @QueryMapping\n    52→    @PreAuthorize(\"hasAuthority('User')\")\n    53→    fun features(\n    54→        @UserId userId: String,\n    55→        @Argument limit: Int?,\n    56→        @Argument offset: Int?,\n    57→    ): List<FeatureResponse> {\n    58→        val response = featureService.getFeatures(userId, limit ?: 20, offset ?: 0)\n    59→        return response.featuresList.map { it.toResponse() }\n    60→    }\n    61→\n    62→    @MutationMapping\n    63→    @PreAuthorize(\"hasAuthority('User')\")\n    64→    fun createFeature(\n    65→        @UserId userId: String,\n    66→        @Argument input: CreateFeatureInput,\n    67→    ): FeatureResponse {\n    68→        val response = featureService.createFeature(userId, input.name)\n    69→        return response.feature.toResponse()\n    70→    }\n    71→}\n    72→```\n    73→\n    74→### 3. GraphQL Service (gRPC Client)\n    75→\n    76→위치: `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/{도메인}/`\n    77→\n    78→```kotlin\n    79→@Service\n    80→class FeatureService {\n    81→    @GrpcClient(\"feature-grpc\")\n    82→    private lateinit var stub: FeatureServiceGrpc.FeatureServiceBlockingStub\n    83→\n    84→    fun getFeatures(userId: String, limit: Int, offset: Int): ListFeaturesResponse {\n    85→        val request = ListFeaturesRequest.newBuilder()\n    86→            .setUserId(userId)\n    87→            .setLimit(limit)\n    88→            .setOffset(offset)\n    89→            .build()\n    90→        return try {\n    91→            stub.listFeatures(request)\n    92→        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {\n    93→            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.trailers!!, e.status.description)\n    94→        }\n    95→    }\n    96→}\n    97→```\n    98→\n    99→### 4. 다중 서비스 어그리게이션\n   100→\n   101→```kotlin\n   102→@QueryMapping\n   103→fun featureWithUser(\n   104→    @UserId userId: String,\n   105→    @Argument featureId: String,\n   106→): FeatureDetailResponse {\n   107→    // 여러 gRPC 서비스 호출 후 조합\n   108→    val feature = featureService.getFeature(featureId)\n   109→    val user = userService.getUserInfo(feature.userId)\n   110→    val score = callService.getMannerScore(feature.userId)\n   111→\n   112→    return FeatureDetailResponse(\n   113→        feature = feature.toResponse(),\n   114→        user = user.toSimpleUser(),\n   115→        mannerScore = score,\n   116→    )\n   117→}\n   118→```\n   119→\n   120→## GraphQL 컨벤션\n   121→\n   122→| 항목 | 규칙 |\n   123→|------|------|\n   124→| Query | 조회 (get, list, search) |\n   125→| Mutation | 생성/수정/삭제 |\n   126→| Type 명 | PascalCase |\n   127→| Input 명 | `{Action}{Domain}Input` |\n   128→| 인증 | `@PreAuthorize(\"hasAuthority('User')\")` |\n   129→| 사용자 ID | `@UserId userId: String` |\n   130→\n   131→## 주의사항\n   132→\n   133→- Controller에서 직접 Repository 접근 금지 (반드시 gRPC Service 경유)\n   134→- 에러 처리: `CustomGraphQLException` 사용\n   135→- N+1 문제: DataLoader 패턴 활용\n   136→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01QGmJTPHysW8usQzHgZ6TpM","session_id":"5a95a97d-5704-4b78-a30a-68dd434e30e8","uuid":"832f062b-70eb-4e6f-abf0-9651b8fc287a"}
